title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Oct 4 2022

description:
Buck gives 20-30% chance Putin uses tactical nukes in Ukraine. General Petraeus on how the U.S. would respond if Russia used nukes. Elon Musk tweets peace plan. Trump statement in support of Herschel Walker. Great moments in covid misinformation. Gas prices rising again, Peter Doocy confronts KJP on it. Herschel Walker has best 24 hours of fundraising. Midterm Red Wave is first step to getting our country back.
